IQANGIGHSALGHETLU PINIGHSALGHETLU

Yataaghqaqunga igaghyamun .
Esghaghtengnga aghmilghiingallu , peghhilghiingallu .

Ggutenka perasaaqanka neneghmeng taaqnemni .
